{"tid":2113817,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"懲教署禁健身書籍 , 好快健身都會違反國安法","createTime":"2020-07-18T11:04:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-18T12:25:52.000Z","uid":25468,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4093ac3b1eb100f58a9724b306363979b310a4f5","tid":2113817,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T11:04:23.000Z","msg":"練咁大隻係咪想作反 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f31f43c575a471d94ae6f923a9443826c52a98f","tid":2113817,"uid":151196,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T11:08:20.000Z","msg":"囚徒健身列為禁書 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05a39ebda2f5d8296f999a674481573f29562056","tid":2113817,"uid":25468,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T11:09:40.000Z","msg":"好人好姐做咩去健身 ?! <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50a6a8ebe8519804ab9b59cdeed8077339ba84ed","tid":2113817,"uid":227275,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T11:10:29.000Z","msg":"ヾ(@^▽^@)ノ"},{"pid":"8711b98ec54199d0f3c43850e4a1f7a32d7ce79f","tid":2113817,"uid":53026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T11:15:25.000Z","msg":"金庸呢？"},{"pid":"799f887feec2230776b85cdddf9aafa8d8eccbb9","tid":2113817,"uid":168366,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T11:33:57.000Z","msg":"驚大家變gay咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d2639b9b0ac10a1fff6bb3ce654841a33c5b512","tid":2113817,"uid":41243,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T11:54:29.000Z","msg":"懲教禁健身書係真定9up"},{"pid":"1d0a3e16e115b17b6707e88163928e0a975777a5","tid":2113817,"uid":250654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T12:02:24.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">Source?</span>"},{"pid":"19bf09dbc444cc5639c3c818028f2ee659902317","tid":2113817,"uid":25468,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1d0a3e16e115b17b6707e88163928e0a975777a5","tid":2113817,"uid":250654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T12:02:24.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">Source?</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T12:11:37.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">有書籍去年成功送進獄中但今年失敗 李家超：懲教署無禁書名單</span><br />\n<br />\n在囚人士有權在獄中看書，但有議員發現有些書籍去年成功送進院所，但今年就不行。保安局局長李家超表示，只有0.1%的書籍不獲批。究竟是什麼書？為何入不到？<br />\n<br />\n去年邵家臻因為兩項煽惑公眾妨擾罪成入獄，他說在獄中其中一個最放鬆的時刻就是閱讀。邵家臻：「我真的是在閱讀時才感到自由。我在獄中163天內，讀了近50本書。例如這本書，有囚犯編號、蓋了印、有日期的。」<br />\n<br />\n不過今年，程翔這本講自己在內地服刑心路歷程的書，懲教署不批准送入獄中。程翔：「我猜可能是人(作者)的問題。我也是屬於那些喜歡批評大陸的人，縱使在上位者沒有(禁書)清單，但是他們揣摩上意，會想：『這本書是否可以的呢？』揣摩上意後，則用更嚴厲的方法處理。」<br />\n<br />\n還有甚麼書不批准送入獄中呢？<strong><span class=\"limegreen\">邵家臻指一些關於反修例運動、監獄情況、寫真集及健身指導的書都不能</span></strong>。「枱上最少有十本書是不能進監獄的書。我想問，催淚香港&hellip;&hellip;」李家超：「我不打算針對每本書刊評論。懲教署並沒有備存所謂的禁止轉交書刊名單，如在2019年，不獲批准的書刊是0.1%，而且每個院所都有刊物審裁委員會，考慮相關因素再作判斷。」<br />\n<br />\n根據監獄規則第56條，一些關於製造槍械 、描述監獄內暴力等的書籍都不批准進內。懲教署以書面回覆，沒有回答為何某一本書之前入到但現在不批准，只是指如果書籍對院所的保安、秩序及紀律有威脅等，就會扣起。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/30634\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F30634&d=G%2B3HFD3c3HuaSfC8k9KTiZvkp%2FM1ZBOvf84g0fLsyFs%3D&h=a798efa1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F30634&h=c03cb32a\" target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/30634</a>"},{"pid":"390229b1bbe767fe4031d8b1712c921d18235900","tid":2113817,"uid":28960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T12:12:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cecb5e691397fa827a8f1afee237637f4a1c35e3","tid":2113817,"uid":240952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T12:21:28.000Z","msg":"//邵家臻指一些關於反修例運動、監獄情況、<span class=\"red\">寫真集</span>及健身指導的書都不能//<br />\n<br />\n點解寫真集都唔得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"867cca7fc499ed682a74ca8efc3857031a475cbd","tid":2113817,"uid":91017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cecb5e691397fa827a8f1afee237637f4a1c35e3","tid":2113817,"uid":240952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T12:21:28.000Z","msg":"//邵家臻指一些關於反修例運動、監獄情況、<span class=\"red\">寫真集</span>及健身指導的書都不能//<br />\n<br />\n點解寫真集都唔得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T12:25:52.000Z","msg":"防止有人火起𨳒屎忽"}]}